---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro'
---
<BaseLayout title="About">
  <section>
    <h2>About this site</h2>
    <p>This small site is a lightweight static landing for the <code>min-android-app-template</code> Flutter repository. It's built with Astro and a Startlight-inspired theme so it's fast and easy to maintain.</p>

    <div class="card">
      <h3>How it works</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Source in <code>/astro</code></li>
        <li>Build uses <code>npm run build</code> to generate a static <code>dist/</code> folder</li>
        <li>CI workflow deploys <code>dist/</code> to GitHub Pages when a GitHub Release is published (or on manual dispatch)</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
